                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-12 mt-4">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100 rounded-pill btn-lg">Confirm Booking</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Terms and Conditions Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="termsModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="termsModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="termsModalLabel">Spa Terms and Conditions</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <h6>Booking Terms</h6>
                <p>By making a spa booking, you agree to the following terms and conditions:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>All spa treatments must be booked at least 24 hours in advance to ensure availability.</li>
                    <li>We require a valid credit card to guarantee your reservation.</li>
                    <li>Please arrive 15 minutes before your scheduled appointment to complete any necessary forms.</li>
                    <li>Late arrivals may result in a shortened treatment time to accommodate other guests.</li>
                    <li>All rates are subject to applicable taxes and service charges.</li>
                </ul>
                <h6>Cancellation Policy</h6>
                <p>We understand that plans change. Please respect our cancellation policy:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Cancellations or changes must be made at least 24 hours prior to your scheduled appointment to avoid charges.</li>
                    <li>Cancellations made less than 24 hours in advance will incur a 50% charge.</li>
                    <li>No-shows will be charged the full treatment price.</li>
                </ul>
                <h6>Health Considerations</h6>
                <p>Your health and safety are our priority:</p>
                <ul>
